                     <decoNote xml:id="d1" type="miniature">
                     <locus target="#10v"/>
                     <desc>The Trinity.</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡</q>
                 </decoNote>    
                     
                     <decoNote xml:id="d2" type="miniature">
                         <locus target="#11r"/>
                         <desc>The archangel Gabriel allows Madḫānina ʾƎgziʾ to ascend miraculously to
                             Dabra Bankʷal.</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ አዕረጎ፡ ለአቡነ፡ መድኃኒነ፡ እግዚእ፡ ውስተ፡ ደብረ፡ በንኮል፡ ቅዱስ፡ ገብርኤል፡</q>
                     </decoNote>
                     
                     <decoNote xml:id="d3" type="miniature">
                         <locus target="#13r"/>
                         <desc>Together with <ref target="#d4"/> and <ref target="#d5"/>, three illustrations showing episodes of the miracle of the lion who
                             was condemned by the saint to carry water for seven years because it
                             devoured the donkey which did this work.</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ ተስአሎ፡ አቡነ፡ መድኃኒነ፡ እግዚእ፡ ለአንበሳ፡ እፎ፡ በልዖ፡ ለአድግ፡
                             ዘይትለአኮ፡ በፀዊረ፡ ማይ።</q>
                     </decoNote>
                     
                     <decoNote xml:id="d4" type="miniature">
                         <locus target="#15v"/>
                         <desc>Together with <ref target="#d3"/> and <ref target="#d5"/>, three illustrations showing episodes of the miracle of the lion who
                             was condemned by the saint to carry water for seven years because it
                             devoured the donkey which did this work.</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ ቀነዮ፡ አቡነ፡ ለአንበሳ። ፯ ዓመተ፡ በፀዊረ፡ ማይ፡</q>
                     </decoNote>
                     
                     <decoNote xml:id="d5" type="miniature">
                         <locus target="#17r"/>
                         <desc>Together with <ref target="#d3"/> and <ref target="#d4"/>, three illustrations showing episodes of the miracle of the lion who
                             was condemned by the saint to carry water for seven years because it
                             devoured the donkey which did this work.</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ወሶበ፡ በጽሐ፡ ተራድኦቱ፡ ለአንበሳ፡ ወረክበ ፡ አርድእተ፡ ዘከመ፡ ባረኮ፡ ወፈነዎ። ኀበ፡
                             ዘቀዳሚ፡ ህላዌሁ፡ ውስተ፡ ገዳም።</q>
                     </decoNote>
                     
                     <decoNote xml:id="d6" type="miniature">
                         <locus target="#24r"/>
                         <desc>The miniature is divided into three episodes.</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ ወረደ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ምስለ፡ ማርያም፡ እሙ፡ ወምስለ፡ ነቢያት፡ ወሐዋርያት።</q>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ወምስለ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ወገብርኤል፡</q>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ ፀለየ፡ አቡነ፡ መድኃኒነ፡ እግዚእ፡ በእንተ፡ ሕንፃ፡ ቤተ፡ መቅደስ።</q>
                     </decoNote>
                     
                     <decoNote xml:id="d7" type="miniature">
                         <locus target="#24v"/>
                         <desc>The 24 Heavenly Priests surround Dabra Bankʷal.</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ አዘዞሙ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ለ፳ወ፬ ካህናተ፡ ሰማይ፡ ምስለ፡ ማዕጠንቶሙ፡ ለደብረ፡
                             በንኰል። ከመ፡ ይዑድዋ።</q>
                     </decoNote>
                     
                     <decoNote xml:id="d8" type="miniature">
                         <locus target="#42"/>
                         <desc>The Virgin with Child (full page).</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡</q>
                     </decoNote>
                     
                     <decoNote xml:id="d9" type="miniature">
                         <locus target="#43v"/>
                         <desc>Together with <ref target="#d10"/>, <ref target="#d11"/> and <ref target="#d12"/>,
                             three illustrations of the salvation of the city of ʾAksum from the
                             Muslim invasion.</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ ወድቀ፡ አቡነ፡ መድኃኒነ፡ እግዚእ፡ ውስተ፡ ጸፍጸፈ፡ አክሱም፡
                             ሶበ፡ መጽኡ፡ ተንባላት፡ ለአማስኖናታ።</q>
                     </decoNote>
                     
                     <decoNote xml:id="d10" type="miniature">
                         <locus target="#44r"/>
                         <desc>Together with <ref target="#d9"/>, <ref target="#d11"/> and <ref target="#d12"/>,
                             three illustrations of the salvation of the city of ʾAksum from the
                             Muslim invasion (full page).</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ መጽኡ፡ ተንባላት፡ ብሔረ፡ አክሱም፡ ለአማስኖ፡</q>
                     </decoNote>
                     
                     <decoNote xml:id="d11" type="miniature">
                         <locus target="#50r"/>
                         <desc>Together with <ref target="#d9"/>, <ref target="#d10"/> and <ref target="#d12"/>,
                             three illustrations of the salvation of the city of ʾAksum from the
                             Muslim invasion (full page).</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ ተዛውዑ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ወአቡነ፡ መድኃኒነ፡ እግዚእ።</q>
                     </decoNote>
                     
                     <decoNote xml:id="d12" type="miniature">
                         <locus target="#50v"/>
                         <desc>Together with <ref target="#d9"/>, <ref target="#d10"/> and <ref target="#d11"/>,
                             three illustrations of the salvation of the city of ʾAksum from the
                             Muslim invasion (full page).</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ አንከሩ፡ ሠራዊት</q>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ አንከረ፡ አቡነ፡ መድኃኒነ፡ እግዚእ፡ ምስለ፡ ደቂቁ፡</q>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ ተግበረ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ግብረ፡ ማኅረስ፡ በእንተ፡ ፍቅሩ፡ ለአቡነ፡</q>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ወንግስትኒ፡ አስተናጽሐት፡ ሣዕረ፡ ወቈጽለ።</q>
                     </decoNote>
                     
                     <decoNote xml:id="d13" type="miniature">
                         <locus target="#64v"/>
                         <desc>The death of ʾAbuna Madḫānina ʾƎgziʾ (full page).</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ መጽአ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ምስለ፡ ወላዲቱ፡ ወምስለ፡ ነቢያት፡ ወሐዋርያት፡ ወምስለ፡ አእላፍ፡ መላእክት፡
                             ሶበ፡ ትወጽእ፡ ነፍሱ፡ ለአቡነ፡ መድኃኒነ፡ እግዚእ፡ ከመ፡ ይትቀበላ፡ በትፍሥሕት።</q>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ አእረፈ፡ አቡነ፡ መድኃኒነ፡ <t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">እግዚእ፡</t:supplied> ወገነዝዎ፡
                             ደቂቁ፡ በብዙኅ፡ ብካይ፡ <sic>ወሰቀቃው፡</sic> በዝማሬ፡ ወበማኅሌት።</q>
                     </decoNote>
                     
                     <decoNote xml:id="d14" type="miniature">
                         <locus target="#65r"/>
                         <desc>Grief over ʾAbuna Madḫānina ʾƎgziʾ.</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ በከዩ፡ በተማኅፅኖ፡ ደቂቁ፡ እለ፡ ሀለዉ፡ ህያ።</q>
                     </decoNote>
                     
                     <decoNote xml:id="d15" type="miniature">
                         <locus target="#69r"/>
                         <desc>ʾAbuna Samuel becomes the successor of ʾAbuna Madḫānina ʾƎgziʾ (full
                             page).</desc>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ ቀደሰ፡ አቡነ፡ ሳሙኤል፡ ውስተ፡ ደብረ፡ በንኰል።</q>
                         <q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ ተራድእዎ፡ ሐዋርያት።</q>
                     </decoNote>
                     
                     
